author: Lobo_da_boss_
title: Good to add another festive key ring to the collection
review:
Opening;

This is a very nice key ring of the 2013 series 11 gingerbread man .

The Minifigure-

 The figure is very nice it has the regular gingerbread man head a very nice torso and arm prints and some great leg printing .

In conclusion-

this my second favorite key ring and I would recommend it to any minifigure fanatic .
